About Us

*About ANUFIX*

ANUFIX is a proprietorship business owned by Prachi (as per PAN records). We provide reliable and professional home services across India.

Our services are divided into two main categories:

*1. Home Appliance Repair & Service*

* AC Repair & Service
* Refrigerator Repair
* Washing Machine Repair
* Microwave Repair
* LED/LCD TV Repair
* Dishwasher and other household appliances

*2. Fabrication Services*

* Welding Work
* Gate & Grill Fabrication
* Custom Metal Work

Our goal is to deliver fast, affordable, and trusted services at your doorstep. Our technicians are experienced and trained to handle a wide range of repair and fabrication needs.

*Why Choose Us?*

* Same Day Service Available
* Skilled Technicians
* Transparent Pricing
* Customer Support

*Note:* ANUFIX is an independent service provider and is not an authorized service center of any brand.